        <description><![CDATA[<h3>Main Features</h3>
<li><span class="NoColor_Bold_None">Fast color output.</span> With a print speed up to 25ppm in both color and black, you no longer have to wait for brilliant color output.</li>
<li><span class="NoColor_Bold_None">Easily print two-sided documents.</span> Using the color laser printer&#39;s duplex printing feature, you can help reduce your printing costs and produce two-sided documents, presentations and brochures.</li>
<li><span class="NoColor_Bold_None">USB Direct Interface.</span> Print PDF and JPEG files directly from your USB flash memory drive without connecting to your PC.</li>
<li><span class="NoColor_Bold_None">High capacity replacement toner cartridges.</span> Spend less time replacing supplies and help reduce operating costs by using high yield replacement toner cartridges.</li>
<li><span class="NoColor_Bold_None">Built-in Networking.</span> Share the HL-4150CDN with everyone on your network via its built-in Ethernet network interface.</li>
<li><span class="NoColor_Bold_None">Flexible paper handling.</span> Use the 250-sheet capacity paper tray for letter or legal paper. Plus, a 50-sheet capacity multi-purpose tray for envelopes or thicker media.</li>
<li><span class="NoColor_Bold_None">Expandable paper capacity.</span> You can increase your total paper capacity to 800 sheets by adding an optional 500-sheet letter/legal paper tray.</li>
<li><span class="NoColor_Bold_None">Brother™ iPrint&amp;Scan.</span> Free app download for wireless printing (JPEG, PDF, web page &amp; e-mail) from your Apple®, Android™ or Windows® Phone 7 (JPEG only) mobile device</li>]]></description>
